The fun day we know as April Fools Day  for most of us with friends playing pranks, turned out to be a nightmare for a guy in Bhopal. READ ALSO: No big deal if a lady makes the first move – Didi Edet Samar Srivastava got the shock of his life when he found his wife in bed with her boyfriend. It was really shocking and Samar did not know what to do. His world was shattered, his wife told him that it was just an April Fools Prank. There was a smile on his face and he thanked his wife for staying so cool even during these difficult times. How the wife’s boyfriend came to their house in such tough lockdown situation is a question the government and police needs to answer.